title: For Sale/Trade:  Complete AR15 Lower - SLR15 by the legendary Territorial Gunsmiths,
postcontent:
This is a rare Territorial Gunsmiths SLR15 lower marked 5.56. No longer made because of how expensive it was to produce them like this. This one has a enhanced single stage and the winter trigger guard. Comes with a ERGO grip and FDE Tapco 6-Position stock . 

These are machined from T6 7075 Aluminum Forgings. They are Cryo treated before and after machining. These have a deep bevel to the magazine well for feeding and feature checkering on the front of the magazine well for grip. The magazine well is broached so the walls are thicker and stronger. The buffer tube threading is reamed and bored which keeps alignment at less than one ten thousandths of an inch variance for proper alignment. These include a Sully Trigger Guard. 

SLR15  - Forged Lower Receiver
The lower receiver of the SLR15 Rifle is forged. This is done for strength because forged is stronger than cast. Forged is what the U.S. Military requires for their issue weapon systems.

•	Magazine Well Grip Enhancement
This allows a more secure grip in all conditions. The grip enhancement is to give the operator superior hold and control when bracing the support hand on the magazine well/front end of the lower receiver.

•	Trigger Over-Travel Adjustment
Trigger creep adjustment with screw, for those who wish to take all the play out of the trigger for a clean crisp break.
